column807: Captivate any room by creating a tranquil
column808: Captivate any room by creating a tranquil ambiance with Canary's mist fountains. While combining modern design with technology, this fountain becomes ideal for use in any space of your home where you like to relax after a hectic day. Diffuse your favorite essential oils and experience extra moisture, softer skin, energizing and peaceful sleep. The cool mist naturally humidifies the air you breathe, while being a perfect addition to your home decor. Add intrigue and a modern look with Canary's line of mist fountains.

column812: Enjoy dual functionality with this classic warmer. Wax melts can be placed in the dish or you may remove the warming dish and place a small jar candle on top of the warming plate.
